# Version control
.git
.gitignore

# Python artifacts
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/*.egg-info
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.env

# Node artifacts
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/build

# Development files
**/*.md
!README.md
.env.example
docker-compose.dev.yml
**/.DS_Store

# Test and lint
**/tests
**/.github

# Logs
**/*.log
